    {
      "id": "69c875716d940c64390b259b",
      "text": "ネットに書き込むときの心得",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774744946,
      "updated": 1774744946
    },
    {
      "id": "69c875710000000000399050",
      "text": "from [2026/03/28]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774744946,
      "updated": 1774744946
    },
    {
      "id": "69c875710000000000399051",
      "text": "ネットに書き込むときの心得",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774744946,
      "updated": 1774744946
    },
    {
      "id": "69c875730000000000399059",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774744948,
      "updated": 1774744949
    },
    {
      "id": "69c875710000000000399052",
      "text": " [ネットに書き込むときの心得]、どこかに書いた気がする",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774744946,
      "updated": 1774744946
    },
    {
      "id": "69c875710000000000399053",
      "text": "  自分を下げる以外のネガティブは発さない",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774744946,
      "updated": 1774744946
    },
    {
      "id": "69c875710000000000399054",
      "text": "   自分を下げるのもあまりやらないほうが良いが、、",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774744946,
      "updated": 1774744946
    },
    {
      "id": "69c889920000000000576749",
      "text": "   ほんとそれ([- 自分のことは棚に上げる])[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1774750097,
      "updated": 1774750143
    },
    {
      "id": "69c875710000000000399055",
      "text": "  人を主語にして評価をしない",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774744946,
      "updated": 1774744946
    },
    {
      "id": "69c875710000000000399056",
      "text": "   ポジティブもなるべく避けたほうがよい",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774744946,
      "updated": 1774744946
    },
    {
      "id": "69c875710000000000399057",
      "text": "    全部ではない気がする、解像度がまだ低い",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774744946,
      "updated": 1774744946
    },
    {
      "id": "69c888370000000000228133",
      "text": "   不用意に他人を主語にしない、ということなのかもしれない[nyarla.icon]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774749751,
      "updated": 1774749766
    },
    {
      "id": "69c888470000000000228134",
      "text": "   \t[nyarla.icon]の失敗はこれに近しい原因がありそう",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774749767,
      "updated": 1774749783
    },
    {
      "id": "69c887b700000000009eb8fe",
      "text": "  [でかい主語で批判]しない、とか？[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774749623,
      "updated": 1774749654
    },
    {
      "id": "69c887c300000000009eb8ff",
      "text": "  \t当たり判定でかすぎて誰かしらの反感を買う",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774749636,
      "updated": 1774749648
    },
    {
